<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 00:33:19 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>哈佛大学同意讨论中东冲突，学生结束抗议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/harvard-students-end-protest-as-university-agrees-to-discuss-middle-east-conflict/0000018f-7950-dd07-adbf-fb72a3f60000</link><description>哈佛大学临时校长艾伦·加伯同意就学生的问题举行抗议者和大学官员的会面</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 23:02:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/harvard-students-end-protest-as-university-agrees-to-discuss-middle-east-conflict/0000018f-7950-dd07-adbf-fb72a3f60000</guid></item><item><title>国防部官员称司法部门拒绝停止对 10 月 7 日事件的调查存在利益冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/defense-officials-cry-conflict-of-interest-over-justices-refusal-to-halt-oct-7-probe/0000018f-78ec-d599-ab8f-7cff5ba00000</link><description>批评者认为，最高法院法官吉拉·坎菲·斯坦尼茨的丈夫、前部长尤瓦尔·斯坦尼茨可能会从国家审计长的调查中受益</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 21:26:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/defense-officials-cry-conflict-of-interest-over-justices-refusal-to-halt-oct-7-probe/0000018f-78ec-d599-ab8f-7cff5ba00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列官员警告称，随着危机加剧，埃及可能会退出人质交易调解努力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-officials-caution-that-egypt-may-pull-out-of-hostage-deal-mediation-efforts/0000018f-78e2-d7a4-adcf-fcf7cc1c0000</link><description>由于开罗拒绝允许人道主义援助通过拉法口岸，以色列和埃及之间的危机正在加深，以色列官员也担心国防和情报合作可能被降级</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 21:16:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-officials-caution-that-egypt-may-pull-out-of-hostage-deal-mediation-efforts/0000018f-78e2-d7a4-adcf-fcf7cc1c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列平民在以色列北部被导弹炸死，五名以色列国防军士兵受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/.premium/israeli-civilian-killed-by-missile-in-northern-israel-five-idf-soldiers-wounded/0000018f-7899-dd07-adbf-fbfbd9200000</link><description>早些时候，火箭弹向马尔基亚地区发射，引发的大火仍在肆虐，其中一枚发射到西加利利的火箭弹击中了一个侦察气球，落入黎巴嫩境内</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 20:21:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/.premium/israeli-civilian-killed-by-missile-in-northern-israel-five-idf-soldiers-wounded/0000018f-7899-dd07-adbf-fbfbd9200000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列最令人沮丧的独立日，内塔尼亚胡利用阵亡者和人质进行宣传</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/.premium/on-a-wretched-independence-day-netanyahu-exploited-the-fallen-and-hostages-for-propaganda/0000018f-787e-df8f-a78f-fdff759c0000</link><description>以色列总理和他的妻子因胆怯而缺席国家独立日仪式，他们预先录制了一段讲话，其中没有任何承担责任的暗示——所有电视网络都乐于播出，就像现场直播一样</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 20:13:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/.premium/on-a-wretched-independence-day-netanyahu-exploited-the-fallen-and-hostages-for-propaganda/0000018f-787e-df8f-a78f-fdff759c0000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙贾巴利亚，没有“后天”战略，以色列士兵再次与哈马斯作战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-gazas-jabalya-with-no-day-after-strategy-israeli-soldiers-fight-hamas-again/0000018f-77e6-df8f-a78f-ffff2f2b0000</link><description>以色列国防军宣布四个多月前“解散”了加沙北部的哈马斯营。现在，以色列军队的整个旅已经返回，他们的经历与他们的对手一样</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 17:24:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-gazas-jabalya-with-no-day-after-strategy-israeli-soldiers-fight-hamas-again/0000018f-77e6-df8f-a78f-ffff2f2b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列拒绝讨论加沙战争“第二天”威胁美国的整个中东战略</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-14/ty-article/.highlight/israels-refusal-to-discuss-day-after-gaza-war-threatens-americas-mideast-strategy/0000018f-77a3-ddbe-addf-77af6eab0000</link><description>以色列在哈马斯事件后的第二天对讨论的顽固态度不仅会危及美国推动进程的努力，而且可能导致大幅倒退，从而产生深远的后果</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 16:14:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-14/ty-article/.highlight/israels-refusal-to-discuss-day-after-gaza-war-threatens-americas-mideast-strategy/0000018f-77a3-ddbe-addf-77af6eab0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 221 天​​：埃及考虑因拉法行动降低与以色列的关系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-221-egypt-mulls-downgrading-relations-with-israel-over-rafah-op/0000018f-77d2-d430-a38f-f7f640e60000</link><description>国际法院将讨论南非周四针对以色列在拉法的进攻而寻求的新紧急措施 ■ 据报道，拜登政府认为以色列在拉法外集中了足够的兵力，以便在未来几天内进行全面进攻 ■ 卡塔尔总理：就释放人质/停火协议进行谈判由于以色列的拉法行动，局势陷入僵局 ■ 以色列极端分子纵火焚烧了两辆加沙救援卡车 ■ 战争进入 221 天​​后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 16:08:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-221-egypt-mulls-downgrading-relations-with-israel-over-rafah-op/0000018f-77d2-d430-a38f-f7f640e60000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡部长加入以色列极右翼“向加沙进军”，要求驱逐巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/netanyahu-ministers-join-israeli-far-right-march-to-gaza-demand-palestinians-expulsion/0000018f-778d-d599-ab8f-7fff00c40000</link><description>国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔呼吁以色列“鼓励”巴勒斯坦人移出加沙地带；两名越过北部边境进入加沙的抗议者被捕</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 15:07:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/netanyahu-ministers-join-israeli-far-right-march-to-gaza-demand-palestinians-expulsion/0000018f-778d-d599-ab8f-7fff00c40000</guid></item><item><title>世界法院将就以色列国防军拉法攻势举行听证会；以色列将于周五提出案件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/world-corut-to-hold-hearings-over-israels-rafah-attacks/0000018f-776a-ddbe-addf-776fbce30000</link><description>南非上周要求联合国法院命令以色列停止拉法入侵后，将于周四在法庭上发言。埃及和土耳其已介入支持此案</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 14:37:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/world-corut-to-hold-hearings-over-israels-rafah-attacks/0000018f-776a-ddbe-addf-776fbce30000</guid></item><item><title>前往加沙的援助车队被以色列极右分子破坏后，巴勒斯坦卡车司机担心安全</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/palestinian-truckers-fear-for-safety-after-gaza-aid-convoy-wrecked-by-far-right-israelis/0000018f-776a-ddbe-addf-776fd8fe0000</link><description>约旦河西岸卡车司机工会的一名司机表示，大约 15 辆卡车被以色列定居者损坏，他们殴打了一些司机，造成了价值约 200 万美元的损失，而以色列军队或警察没有干预</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 14:28:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/palestinian-truckers-fear-for-safety-after-gaza-aid-convoy-wrecked-by-far-right-israelis/0000018f-776a-ddbe-addf-776fd8fe0000</guid></item><item><title>两辆运载人道主义援助物资前往加沙的卡车在约旦河西岸起火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/.premium/two-trucks-with-humanitarian-aid-bound-for-gaza-set-on-fire-in-the-west-bank/0000018f-75f7-ddbe-addf-77ff80bb0000</link><description>据记录，右翼活动分子将援助卡车上的食物扔在地上，其中两辆卡车后来被烧毁。以色列警方和以色列国防军互相指责对方执法不力，但一名高级安全官员表示，骚乱者收到了“内部消息”</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 09:19:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/.premium/two-trucks-with-humanitarian-aid-bound-for-gaza-set-on-fire-in-the-west-bank/0000018f-75f7-ddbe-addf-77ff80bb0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争中，以色列和平阵营是面临灭亡还是复活？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/.premium/amid-the-gaza-war-is-israels-pro-peace-camp-facing-extinction-or-resurrection/0000018f-7172-d7ad-abdf-f57eecf90000</link><description>即使没有向参加以色列反战和反内塔尼亚胡抗议活动的大批人群投射左翼反占领幻想，仍然可以肯定地说，越来越多的犹太以色列人对其政府的好战方式感到失望 — — 以至于他们可以可以想象与反抗的、持久的左派达成共同目标</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 09:15:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/.premium/amid-the-gaza-war-is-israels-pro-peace-camp-facing-extinction-or-resurrection/0000018f-7172-d7ad-abdf-f57eecf90000</guid></item><item><title>报道：真主党指挥官在黎巴嫩南部以色列无人机袭击中丧生，两人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article-live/u-s-germany-slam-right-wing-israelis-attack-on-gaza-bound-aid-convoy/0000018f-74c8-dd07-adbf-fffa73560000</link><description>以色列平民在北部边境城镇被导弹炸死，五名以色列国防军士兵受伤 ■ 四名以色列国防军士兵在加沙战斗中重伤 ■ 联合国表示，随着以色列国防军坦克深入拉法，超过 50 万人逃离加沙北部拉法 ■ 极右翼内塔尼亚胡部长领导游行呼吁重新安置加沙地带 ■ 报道：埃及官员称开罗考虑降级与以色列的外交关系</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 01:59:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article-live/u-s-germany-slam-right-wing-israelis-attack-on-gaza-bound-aid-convoy/0000018f-74c8-dd07-adbf-fffa73560000</guid></item><item><title>联合国称修改数据来源后加沙总死亡人数保持不变</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/un-says-total-number-of-gaza-deaths-unchanged-after-halving-toll-of-children-killed/0000018f-739f-dff1-a9af-73bf60770000</link><description>联合国人道主义办公室公布的数据减少了加沙地带妇女和儿童的死亡人数。联合国表示，新数据反映了已确认死亡的总人数，不包括约 10,000 名额外的不明死亡人数</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 21:04:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-14/ty-article/un-says-total-number-of-gaza-deaths-unchanged-after-halving-toll-of-children-killed/0000018f-739f-dff1-a9af-73bf60770000</guid></item><item><title>人质家属举行另类独立日仪式</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-13/ty-article/.premium/hostages-families-hold-alternative-independence-day-ceremony/0000018f-72f4-db28-ab8f-f3f5ab780000</link><description>亲属们扑灭火焰以表达他们被遗弃的感受，这与他们拒绝参加的官方仪式上点燃火炬形成鲜明对比</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 17:52:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-13/ty-article/.premium/hostages-families-hold-alternative-independence-day-ceremony/0000018f-72f4-db28-ab8f-f3f5ab780000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯指责以色列在车辆罢工中杀害两名联合国工作人员；以色列国防军调查事件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-13/ty-article/.premium/hamas-accuses-israel-of-killing-two-un-workers-in-vehicle-strike/0000018f-72c5-dd07-adbf-fbf730670000</link><description>哈马斯声称以色列杀害了两名“携带联合国旗帜和识别标志旅行”的人</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 16:58:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-13/ty-article/.premium/hamas-accuses-israel-of-killing-two-un-workers-in-vehicle-strike/0000018f-72c5-dd07-adbf-fbf730670000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列，第 220 天：以色列抗议者破坏了前往加沙的救援卡车</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-220-israeli-protesters-damage-aid-trucks-en-route-to-gaza/0000018f-72a2-dd07-adbf-fbf223780000</link><description>加沙人报道，以色列坦克进一步深入贾巴利亚，穿过拉法郊区的主要高速公路 ■ 《纽约时报》报道，辛瓦尔很可能从未离开汗尤尼斯下面的隧道 ■ 美国驻以色列特使表示，美以关系没有发生根本性变化 ■ 五名士兵，以色列国防军称，自周六以来，国防部雇员在加沙的战斗事件中受重伤 ■ 这是战争 220 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 16:46:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-220-israeli-protesters-damage-aid-trucks-en-route-to-gaza/0000018f-72a2-dd07-adbf-fbf223780000</guid></item><item><title>被释放的以色列人质在电视采访中描述了哈马斯视频的制作过程</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-13/ty-article/.premium/released-israeli-hostage-describes-how-gaza-videos-were-made-in-tv-interview/0000018f-7250-d7ad-abdf-f65ea34d0000</link><description>梅拉夫·塔尔告诉第 12 频道新闻，当她与其他人一起被巴勒斯坦伊斯兰圣战组织扣押时，拍摄了几个小时的镜头，其中大部分未公开</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 15:36:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-13/ty-article/.premium/released-israeli-hostage-describes-how-gaza-videos-were-made-in-tv-interview/0000018f-7250-d7ad-abdf-f65ea34d0000</guid></item><item><title>56年前，一艘以色列潜艇失踪。船上有我的邻居阿里克</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/56-years-ago-an-israeli-submarine-disappeared-on-board-was-my-neighbor-arik/0000018f-71d0-d7ad-abdf-f5de0d7d0000</link><description>我的邻居 Arik Feingold 与其他达喀尔船员一起失踪时年仅 22 岁。以色列阵亡士兵纪念碑之间的旅程揭示了我们感知死亡、记忆和丧亲之痛的方式</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 14:05:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/56-years-ago-an-israeli-submarine-disappeared-on-board-was-my-neighbor-arik/0000018f-71d0-d7ad-abdf-f5de0d7d0000</guid></item></channel></rss>